Burda Raises 2011 Revenue Forecast by 5%, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-10-12T06:10:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/burda-raises-2011-revenue-forecast-by-5-handelsblatt-says.html
German media group Hubert Burda
Media Holding GmbH & Co. raised its 2011 revenue forecast by 5
percent, to 2.1 billion euros ($2.9 billion) from 2 billion
euros, Handelsblatt reported, citing an interview with Chief
Executive Officer Paul-Bernhard Kallen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
